{"tid":2056211,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有無Power BI高手","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T07:23:19.000Z","uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec9ce4c2d4c12667637e095befa83caa8354085","tid":2056211,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"我本身用開Tableau, 但新公司要用power BI,，但好多野唔識做返出黎，想請教下高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個data係customer visit record, 最重要係有兩行Column，Date同Customer Name<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0cKLsd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0cKLsd.jpg&h=228e7b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以做到好似下圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYieoeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYieoeG.jpg&h=afa5a446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nX axis係date (Month-Day)<br />\nY axis係customer name<br />\n圖入面既交叉就係果個customer係果一日visit過<br />\n<br />\n有無高手教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060010a97d5efd7c9929e806b75de961d77df7e4","tid":2056211,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"用tableau好易整，但power BI我整左好耐都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97244f87b82df1d12202bd293a5de91d12e72dc","tid":2056211,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2701e79c3bd56e866526b80bc436863558b30c05","tid":2056211,"uid":48623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"執柒左 Power BI 啦，勁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de50a680c80900a81a13c484503df5b1